Messages.Value: Thank you for calling our travel agency, my name is Lily Young. How may I assist you today?
Hi Lily, my name is John Smith and I recently traveled from Boston to Chicago and I am quite dissatisfied with my experience.
I'm sorry to hear that, John. Can you tell me a little bit more about what happened?
Yes, my luggage was lost during the flight and I had trouble tracking it down and reclaiming it. It was a major inconvenience and I think something needs to be done about it.
I understand your frustration, John. Let me look into this for you. Can you please provide me with your flight details and reservation number?
Yes, I flew with American Airlines on May 5th from Boston Logan International Airport to O'Hare International Airport in Chicago. My reservation number is 123456789.
Thank you, John. I will reach out to American Airlines on your behalf to track down your luggage and assist with the reclaiming process. Is there anything else I can help with?
No, that's all. Thank you for your help, Lily.
